{"tid":485181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得欄后畀人摸過係真, 只係「創傷」個part有問題","createTime":"2017-11-30T17:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T06:05:22.000Z","uid":76115,"like":272,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"4f26a59b0835de4ca1a1ea5e135b65c736892e7e","tid":485181,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:15:58.000Z","msg":"發生之後繼續正常聯絡八年, 最可能解釋係佢自己都當左件事係青春期一種性探索, 多過乜野陰影創傷<br />\n<br />\n到呢幾個月突然間美國有#MeToo, 又成村奧運選手出來話畀教練性侵, 女人一要跟風人有我有, 二鐘意做受害者, 咪覺得我堂堂十四歲畀人摸過, 咁都唔出來寫篇#MeToo咪好撚蝕底<br />\n<br />\n見到搞到咁大淋病一哥都話幫手, 個個想釘死人渣教練, 先至自己都過意唔去所以唔肯配合黑警調查<br />\n<br />\n如果真係成單作出來嘅話佢就係教科書級psychopath, 仲危險過周唔知乜亮, 但我覺得唔太可能, 似係女人啲鳩屎性格加埋facebook自戀搏關注文化先搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c307875f548968b3d626b742d9a08f9dd0d409","tid":485181,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3a6d7c9003fd67e45cd7b67d1284efed9a2785","tid":485181,"uid":76744,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"d0691769c0966c4c27ef1eedb865ebbf8b0f8007","tid":485181,"uid":45788,"like":7,"dislike":71,"score":-64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"樓主Up乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c855f1a8f3046a47c090eec35a8fbde87d11cde2","tid":485181,"uid":14918,"like":144,"dislike":0,"score":144,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主Up乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明佢up乜<br />\n女人既思維就係咁了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一時victim playing 想跟風 但玩大左就想縮沙"},{"pid":"521ced1669e4a8dccd480933f87a202249d20885","tid":485181,"uid":21488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:35:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主Up乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明佢up乜<br />\n女人既思維就係咁了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一時victim playing 想跟風 但玩大左就想縮沙</blockquote><br />\nYup"},{"pid":"9a36032556a8fa9bc463a779b1d7e84356ca3ba0","tid":485181,"uid":36543,"like":47,"dislike":19,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主Up乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呂畜比人摸果陣根本好撚enjoy<br />\n到最近女權撚係咁炒作咪跟埋一份風<br />\n點知玩大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有料既一早報左警啦仲上fb up 咩<br />\n同食狗肉果單野一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d320b4554c1fdfa501bc90e420094de1389093e","tid":485181,"uid":57705,"like":4,"dislike":12,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82329307f27cf37ac8e80a67dc6e36ec5cab0b03","tid":485181,"uid":51129,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T17:48:18.000Z","msg":"但係校方話三星期前已經收到料<br />\n如果佢個Facebook post只係跟風玩下，唔係存心爆料嘅，何必提前三星期放風俾學校？"},{"pid":"a1d6edec5c95de82b9b55aae21082ca66f3cfab6","tid":485181,"uid":45788,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:07:00.000Z","msg":"都係個句<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/01/020650_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F01%2F020650_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=211db8f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa507915461c089c9220beeef9576f4ca0dda946","tid":485181,"uid":95123,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:09:15.000Z","msg":"睇左做比人摸後欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a394ac5bd16ba066137d686673cd50d2803ee3","tid":485181,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1999</blockquote><br />\n真係幾1999<br />\nSorry打多次<br />\n<br />\n佢畀教練摸完之後八年一直有聯絡, 最可能就係佢自己都無當件事係創傷, 只係青春期一次性探索嘅經歷<br />\n<br />\n到呢幾個月, 佢見到美國有#MeToo運動, 又有奧運選手集體話教練性侵, 女人性格鐘意跟風, 鐘意做受害者, 咪覺得我自己十四歲都畀人摸過, 一於寫返篇#MeToo唔好蝕底<br />\n<br />\n點知而家見到搞到咁大, 淋病一哥都話幫手, facebook瘋狂公審個教練, 自己都過意唔去, 所以先唔配合黑警調查<br />\n<br />\n如果成單野真係佢作出來嘅話, 佢就係教科書級psychopath, 仲危險過周凱亮, 但我覺得無乜可能, 似係女人啲鳩屎性格加埋facebook自戀搏關注文化先搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfd0fe967e965444e2a5fc6e569db975934c4fd","tid":485181,"uid":76115,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常黎講雖然冇開名<br />\n但網民稍為起下底已經知係指邊個<br />\n傳媒仲打埋去<br />\n如果係真係冇做既應該好大反應否認左<br />\n但個前教練而家係驚講錯野唔咁答，身有屎多<br />\n<br />\n爆料又唔肯同警方合作<br />\n可能係心入面覺得冇可能入到罪唔想搞掛<br />\n兼且一開波被人摸撚完仲同人慶祝生日，俾人個感覺又真係好怪</blockquote><br />\n雖然人類心理係好複雜<br />\n但如果「創傷」完之後可以避都唔避下, 仲要唔係一排而係足足八年, 咁「創傷」咪變到咩標準都無哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9811bce76bcd1d1838467070aa010f34f7d95b4","tid":485181,"uid":2023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:38:06.000Z","msg":"樓主好中point<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d545cff355fd087003e73ad0a6865da673316f92","tid":485181,"uid":74020,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T18:43:36.000Z","msg":"個教練做就一定有做架啦，唔係一早死出黎澄清啦，我唔